1. Persona is about customer experience and how to make them feel comfortable
while using the product.
2. Our main aim with the following walking system is to make it hassle free for
the elderly and the visually impaired.
3. Integrating vibrating claw controllers makes it easier for the blind and the
elderly with vision problems.
4. Taking feedback and trying to make it comfortable for the customers and
accommodating new changes will always be priority
